Package com.github.tadukoo.view.components.interfaces

Interface TButton

All Superinterfaces:
HasDisabledTextPaint, HasSelectAndFocusPaints, HasSizablePaints, Shaped, TComponent
All Known Implementing Classes:
TadukooButton
public interface TButton
extends TComponent, HasSelectAndFocusPaints, HasDisabledTextPaint
This is a generic interface to be used in Buttons. It extends TComponent, along with HasSelectAndFocusPaints and HasDisabledTextPaint, in order to cover the interfaces needed for the customizations for a Button.
Version:
Alpha v.0.3
Author:
Logan Ferree (Tadukoo)
